20:28.125 --> 20:29.708
Oh, sorry Sam.

20:29.917 --> 20:31.083
That bloody dog.

20:31.833 --> 20:33.917
That's the last fuckin' time,
I'm tellin' you.

20:35.083 --> 20:36.375
Sorry lord, for swearing.

20:36.458 --> 20:39.083
It's alright boss, you can take
Lucy with you to town?

20:39.917 --> 20:43.167
Because that Harry fella,
he was looking at her funny way.

20:44.167 --> 20:45.167
Yeah, 'course.

20:45.583 --> 20:46.792
Take 'em back to mother.

20:47.125 --> 20:49.542
Her mother can look
after her for little while.

20:50.167 --> 20:51.167
Yeah, alright Sam.

20:52.167 --> 20:53.167
Listen, ah

20:54.667 --> 20:57.833
I'll be away two or three weeks.
