21:21.208 --> 21:22.208
Something wrong?

21:51.833 --> 21:52.833
Whitefella, boss.

21:53.125 --> 21:54.542
Shut your mouth, philomac.

22:01.667 --> 22:03.167
- Right there?
- Gidday.

22:05.292 --> 22:06.458
I'm Harry march.

22:06.625 --> 22:08.417
Just taken over north creek station.

22:08.875 --> 22:10.208
