22:23.875 --> 22:25.167
Oh, good on you mate.

22:25.583 --> 22:26.583
Mick Kennedy.

22:26.875 --> 22:28.375
Urn, philomac!

22:29.208 --> 22:31.250
Go inside, get us a couple
of pannikins, will you?

22:32.083 --> 22:33.167
