22:46.792 --> 22:49.792
Yeah, fair bit of work for one bloke.

22:50.042 --> 22:51.042
Yeah.

22:52.708 --> 22:55.583
I had Fred Smith's blackfella
give me a day's work.

22:55.667 --> 22:56.667
- Did you?
- Yeah.

22:56.750 --> 22:57.958
- Sam?
- Yeah.

22:58.875 --> 23:00.458
No, he did a half-arsed job, too.

23:03.125 --> 23:04.542
Yeah, well

23:04.833 --> 23:07.542
he's a bit of a fuckin'
myall breed, that one.

