23:34.292 --> 23:35.292
Yeah.

23:40.583 --> 23:41.583
Yeah.

23:43.250 --> 23:44.333
Who's that blackfella?

23:44.417 --> 23:46.917
Keep your own business
to yourself philomac. Shut up.

23:47.500 --> 23:48.780
Don't talk when men are talking.

23:48.833 --> 23:50.708
You too, Archie. Shut up. Stop laughing.

24:30.333 --> 24:31.708
You grab my saddle bag, boy.

24:36.875 --> 24:38.000
