24:57.458 --> 24:58.458
Come here.

25:00.583 --> 25:02.625
Whoa, whoa, whoa! No, no, no, no!

25:03.417 --> 25:04.583
No, no, no, no, no, no!

25:04.875 --> 25:05.750
- No, no!
- Shut up!

25:05.833 --> 25:07.042
- Hey, hey, hey!
- Come on.

25:07.167 --> 25:08.607
- Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey!
