29:31.875 --> 29:34.500
Come on! I know you're in there!

29:36.625 --> 29:39.542
Fred Smith? You harbouring a prisoner?

29:39.625 --> 29:41.042
- Boss!
- Shut up!

29:43.375 --> 29:44.292
Fred!

29:44.375 --> 29:45.625
No-one here boss.

29:45.750 --> 29:48.458
You let him out,
or I'm gonna come in and get him!

29:51.625 --> 29:52.625
Fred!

29:52.667 --> 29:54.000
Town! He gone town!

29:54.333 --> 29:56.542
- Where's Fred?
- He's gone town!

30:03.167 --> 30:05.542
Ah here he is. The myall breed.

30:05.625 --> 30:07.333
Now you give me that boy you're hiding!

30:07.792 --> 30:09.375
