36:21.958 --> 36:23.000
What are you looking at?

37:03.750 --> 37:04.750
Sergeant!

37:05.833 --> 37:07.333
Sergeant!

37:07.417 --> 37:08.417
What?

37:09.250 --> 37:10.417
