37:14.750 --> 37:15.750
Message?

37:16.875 --> 37:19.083
Better be from his royal bloody highness.

37:31.875 --> 37:33.167
Constable minty.

37:38.542 --> 37:40.708
Sorry sir, there's been a shooting.

37:49.292 --> 37:50.708
Get up! Fuck off.

37:53.000 --> 37:54.042
Doc already gone?

37:54.417 --> 37:55.417
Yeah, this morning.

37:57.625 --> 37:58.833
Saddle up the horses, eh?

37:59.000 --> 38:00.000
Yes, sarge.

39:29.917 --> 39:30.917
Uncle.

39:34.625 --> 39:36.375
Where the fuck have you been, philomac?

39:37.500 --> 39:39.000
Where the fuck have you been?

39:40.000 --> 39:41.417
Don't look at him. Look here!

39:45.208 --> 39:46.208
Where have you been?

