40:23.167 --> 40:24.167
Shot in the head.

40:27.917 --> 40:28.917
Did you see it?

40:29.208 --> 40:30.208
No.

40:33.542 --> 40:35.042
That blackfella Sam killed him.

40:39.000 --> 40:40.042
You see it happen?

40:50.042 --> 40:51.167
You didn't see it happen?

40:52.875 --> 40:53.875
