the pleasure of meeting.

41:56.292 --> 41:58.333
A man who, like myself, was a soldier.

41:59.875 --> 42:01.583
Fought for king and country.

42:02.458 --> 42:03.667
Put his life on the line.

42:07.417 --> 42:08.875
They shall not grow old

42:10.000 --> 42:11.625
as we that are left grow old.

42:13.042 --> 42:14.958
Age shall not weary them or the...

42:15.708 --> 42:16.833
Years condemn.

42:18.167 --> 42:19.583
At the going down of the sun,

42:20.417 --> 42:21.542
and in the morning,

42:23.500 --> 42:24.833
