back alive, sergeant.

43:34.000 --> 43:35.083
What are you doing?

43:40.125 --> 43:41.845
No, you're not.
You're over with the horses.

43:42.792 --> 43:43.792
Go on, get.

43:49.750 --> 43:51.583
That was a bit harsh, wasn't it sergeant?

43:53.500 --> 43:56.042
Crown wants him to look after
the horses, not just track.

43:59.042 --> 44:01.792
