Ls he your son?

48:44.292 --> 48:45.292
What's his name?

48:47.458 --> 48:48.458
Philomac.

48:48.917 --> 48:50.000
Philomac, yeah.

48:52.000 --> 48:53.720
You make sure you look
after him, won't you?

48:55.333 --> 48:57.708
Otherwise I'm going to
have to take him away.

50:05.833 --> 50:06.833
Fuck.

51:15.167 --> 51:16.250
Who owns this land?

52:38.500 --> 52:39.500
- Boss!
- What?

52:39.583 --> 52:42.083
- Boss?
- Ha! Go on!

53:35.500 --> 53:36.500
Jesus Christ.

53:37.750 --> 53:38.750
Go! Go on!

