- He's dead.

54:35.708 --> 54:36.708
We gotta go!

54:39.250 --> 54:40.810
Listen, we need to go back for him now!

54:41.250 --> 54:42.250
You bastard!

54:42.542 --> 54:43.750
You set us up, didn't ya?

54:44.958 --> 54:46.309
