01:00:32.417 --> 01:00:33.417
Nuh.

01:00:34.375 --> 01:00:37.000
Been out two weeks. Got a station to run.

01:00:38.167 --> 01:00:39.208
Fuck off, then.

01:00:39.917 --> 01:00:40.958
Go on, fuck off!

01:00:45.750 --> 01:00:46.750
