01:00:59.625 --> 01:01:00.500
Go home.

01:01:00.583 --> 01:01:01.583
Come on, Archie.

01:01:04.667 --> 01:01:05.667
Go on.

01:01:05.750 --> 01:01:06.750
Go on.

01:06:00.792 --> 01:06:01.833
Shut up, philomac.

01:06:02.333 --> 01:06:03.333
