- Hey!

01:14:55.083 --> 01:14:56.375
Bloody amazing.

01:15:01.125 --> 01:15:04.125
The Kelly gang escapes
the long arm of the law.

01:15:20.917 --> 01:15:22.833
I couldn't fuckin' get him.

01:15:29.375 --> 01:15:30.667
